scripts.bin:win: ncc build -o build/lib index.js && pkg --target node16-win-x64  -o build/agent.exe ./build/lib/index.js && npm run jfrog:push
scripts.bin:mac: ncc build -o build/lib index.js && pkg --target node16-mac-arm64 -o build/agent-bin ./build/lib/index.js
scripts.bin:mac-zip: ncc build -o build/lib index.js && pkg --target node16-mac-arm64 --compress GZip -o build/agent-zip ./build/lib/index.js
scripts.bin:mac-bro: ncc build -o build/lib index.js && pkg --target node16-mac-arm64 --compress Brotli -o build/agent-brotli ./build/lib/index.js
